snippet: The Courier  Enquirer comments upon the iniquity of the late Cuban outrage in all its details of origin and development, especially referring to the bonds issued by the invading leaders, to be re-deemed from the fruits of the seizure of the island...
lead_paragraph: The Courier Enquirer comments upon the iniquity of the late Cuban outrage in all its details of origin and development, especially referring to the bonds issued by the invading leaders, to be re-deemed from the fruits of the seizure of the island fruits to be acquired by no other title than that which brute force confers.
